  "title": "A crescent moon-like UFO spotted in Curitiba {2000]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/14/a-crescent-moon-like-ufo-spotted-in-curitiba-2000/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-sh",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>JUNE 6th, 2000</strong>. Time: 11:50 pm. Duration: 7 minutes. On a clear night in the center of Colombo, State of Paraná, three people observed an unidentified flying object in the shape of a &#8220;crescent moon&#8221; and orange color hovering &#8220;just above the horizon&#8221;. The UFO emitted a very clear orange light, but this light &#8220;decreased in intensity as if smoke was involved in the object&#8221;. The witness who informed the sighting to COMDABRA [Brazilian Aerospace Defense Command] also reported having some knowledge about Ufology.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.577. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre avistamento de ovni na cidade de Colombo, Estado do Paraná”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
